p.cl:
With these witnesses . . . abbot of Newbattle; Robert Avenel, and Gervase his
                  son; William de Somerville; John son of Orm, William his son;
                  Glai nephew of Robert Avenel; Gernun; Nicholas son of Adam;
                  Peter, parson of Morebattle; W . . . of Hownam.
